gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 116, Bulls 102
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Bulls, 116-102. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander recorded a game-high 40 points, to go along with 12 assists and five rebounds for the Thunder, with Isaiah Joe adding 20 points (5-7 3PM) off the bench in the victory. DeMar DeRozan tallied 25 points and six assists for the Bulls in the losing effort. The Thunder have won six games in a row and improve to 11-4 in the regular season, while the Bulls fall to 5-11.
